    "attributes": {
        "action": "Council tax reduction for freehold properties paying Management Companies",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The Government should reduce Council Tax rates for freehold properties where 'Management Companies' are paid for maintenance of un-adopted roads/utilities, when these would normally be covered by the local authority. We believe paying both full council tax and a 'Management Company' fee is unfair.",
